<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Weißenburg</head><p>Der Rat benachrichtigt die Stadt Weißenburg vom Tod König Ruprechts I.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_119" id="59r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_119_r2l29"><expan>weiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_119_r2l30">Als vvir ew vor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> winſheim briefs ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l31">geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ſıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>leid<ex>er</ex></expan> alſo ıſt das vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l32"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> etc vt <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> et <expan>Sweinf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_119" id="59r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Als wir ew vor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Winsheim briefs ein
                            <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> gesant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>sid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>leid<ex>er</ex></expan> also ist, das uns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> etc. ut <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> et
                                <expan>Sweinf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
